@using WarsztatTuningowy.Extensions
@using WarsztatTuningowy.Models.Enums
@model WarsztatTuningowy.Models.Domain.Order
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = $"Edytuj zlecenie #{Model.Id}";
    var currentGoal = (int)Model.TuningGoal;
}

<nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li class="breadcrumb-item">
            <a asp-action="Index">Zlecenia</a>
        </li>
        <li class="breadcrumb-item">
            <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@Model.Id">
                Zlecenie #@Model.Id
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="breadcrumb-item active">Edycja</li>
    </ol>
</nav>

<div class="page-header">
    <div style="font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;
          color:var(--gray-500);text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:.5rem">
        Edycja rekordu
    </div>
    <h1>Edytuj zlecenie #@Model.Id</h1>
</div>

<div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header fw-bold">Dane zlecenia</div>
            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <form asp-action="Edit" method="post">
                    <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly"
                         class="alert alert-danger mb-3"></div>
                    <input type="hidden" asp-for="Id" />

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="VehicleId" class="form-label">
                            Pojazd
                        </label>
                        <select asp-for="VehicleId" class="form-select" asp-items="ViewBag.VehicleId">
                            <option value="">— wybierz pojazd —</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label fw-semibold">Cel tuningu</label>
                        <div class="card p-3 mb-2">
                            <div class="text-muted small mb-2">
                                Stopień chiptuningu (wybierz jeden)
                            </div>
                            @foreach (var stage in new[] 
                            {
                                (1, "Stage 1"), (2, "Stage 2"), (4, "Stage 3")
                            })
                            {
                                <div class="form-check">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="tuningGoals"
                                           value="@stage.Item1" id="stage@stage.Item1"
                                    @((currentGoal & stage.Item1) != 0 ? "checked" : "") />
                                    <label class="form-check-label" for="stage@stage.Item1">
                                        @stage.Item2
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                        <div class="card p-3">
                            <div class="text-muted small mb-2">
                                Dodatki (można łączyć)
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="tuningGoals"
                                       value="8" id="mechanical"
                                @((currentGoal & 8) != 0 ? "checked" : "") />
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="mechanical">
                                    Modyfikacje mechaniczne
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="tuningGoals"
                                       value="16" id="visual"
                                @((currentGoal & 16) != 0 ? "checked" : "") />
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="visual">
                                    Modyfikacje wizualne
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="EstimatedHours" class="form-label">
                            Szacowany czas (h)
                        </label>
                        <input asp-for="EstimatedHours" class="form-control" placeholder="np. 8 lub 8,5" />
                        <span asp-validation-for="EstimatedHours" class="text-danger small"></span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="DefaultMechanicId" class="form-label">
                            Domyślny mechanik
                        </label>
                        <select asp-for="DefaultMechanicId" class="form-select" asp-items="ViewBag.DefaultMechanicId">
                            <option value="">— wybierz mechanika —</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <div class="form-check form-switch">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" asp-for="DepositPaid" role="switch" />
                            <label class="form-check-label" asp-for="DepositPaid">
                                Zaliczka wpłacona
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="d-flex gap-2 justify-content-end
                        pt-3 border-top">
                        <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@Model.Id" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                            Anuluj
                        </a>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                            ✓ Zapisz zmiany
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @{
        await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");
    }
}